T1  - Body imaging and sexual behavior in lean women with polycystic ovary syndrome.
T3  - Comment in: J Sex Med. 2014 Jul;11(7):1882-3 PMID: 24636134 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24636134]
