T1  - Predictive factors of health-related quality of life in patients with polycystic ovary syndrome: a structural equation modeling approach.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2013.06.043
A1  - Bazarganipour, Fatemeh
A1  - Ziaei, Saeide
A1  - Montazeri, Ali
