T1  - Polycystic ovary syndrome is associated with negatively variable impacts on domains of health-related quality of life: evidence from a meta-analysis.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2011.05.072
A1  - Li, Yanan
A1  - Li, Yan
A1  - Yu Ng, Ernest Hung
